title: T.S.Eliot-Synopsis of Commentary on The Waste Land July 2016
description:
Just as it says. Salient observations collected for comparison and for the enlightenment both of first time and long-standing readers of the poem. This is the July 2016 update in pdf., mobi & epub (look in 01), together with other pertinent material.

(And a big if belated shout out to the uploader of 'T S Eliot book pack 7752542 TPB' from which I have taken most of Eliot's prose that is included in the torrent - find others in the folder 'Some Eliot Torrents')
